              </summary>
              <div class="px-8 py-6">
                <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[14px] p-6 flex flex-col gap-6">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-text-body leading-5 mb-3">After receiving court approval:</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
